<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7751> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7751" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor 76. See MRR 2.93. Sent by Sertorius ca. 75 as envoy to Mithridates, who gave him a command in the Third Mithridatic War (Plut. Sert. 24.2; Luc. 8.5; called # in App. Mith. 77).\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7751 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4342> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4342" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Sertorius in Spain, having probably come with Perperna (Liv. 91, fr. 22W; cf. Plut. Sert. 24.3; Luc. 8.5; App. Mith. 77 #, cf. Münzer, RE)." ;
	dprr:hasID 4342 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10434> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10434" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/21> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "App. Mith. 77, Oros. 6.2, 6.21-22. Legatus and 'strategos' to Mithridates between being sent to him in 75 and his execution by Lucullus in 73." ;
	dprr:hasID 10434 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10433> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10433" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/32> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Probably joined Sertorians with Perperna in 77." ;
	dprr:hasID 10433 .
